{"tid":809522,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我幾鍾意花師奶呢類型嘅女仔","createTime":"2018-09-07T08:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T15:21:09.000Z","uid":64694,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"515f6dc36c3692b76e16160f8312e5827b59482a","tid":809522,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T08:59:24.000Z","msg":"雖然睇落神神化化、癲癲得得咁，做事誇張、唔理周圍人嘅目光做事，但我覺得咁樣好真性情、好有膽識，唔驚其他人，身為一個毒撚，我自己平時出街唔會夠膽咁做，但我好羨慕可以做到咁嘅女仔，同嗰啲平時好假、扮晒嘢、口嗰句同心嗰句唔同、背後先講真話壞話嘅女仔唔同，我有時覺得花老爺好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說花老爺算唔算係毒撚嚟？我見佢平時好似唔係點講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5fc477ec9931c6f98ce77071cd75cfb4ba8062","tid":809522,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:26:48.000Z","msg":"別怪他"},{"pid":"ebef014a9e48fa2154b240f208bd586a0441e687","tid":809522,"uid":10635,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:39:04.000Z","msg":"盧覓雪應該好岩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2999e21b74d835e9872601819b9a17e531d43048","tid":809522,"uid":20428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:54:16.000Z","msg":"同好"},{"pid":"5aea7576d894b0e7021240333b23aa05f9218c1e","tid":809522,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:58:26.000Z","msg":"樓主係陸浩明？"},{"pid":"641b62ccae0e9e98ae684ab5e1e275f5abdab06d","tid":809522,"uid":66076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T14:34:37.000Z","msg":"動漫台棋靈王 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac620b07b165911759f19641bb2356e1cec7508","tid":809522,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T14:44:29.000Z","msg":"戀母情義結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6615e139f573f05784a5d5f57cba12dde6270a0","tid":809522,"uid":2223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cite